                            <comment id="17566998" author="enricomi" created="Thu, 14 Jul 2022 22:17:04 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=srielau&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;srielau&quot;&gt;srielau&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=cloud_fan&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;cloud_fan&quot;&gt;cloud_fan&lt;/a&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17617460" author="ivan.sadikov" created="Fri, 14 Oct 2022 04:27:53 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This is by design if I am not mistaken. Such columns need to be escaped, for example, this works just fine:&#160;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
Seq((0)).toDF(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;the.id&quot;&lt;/span&gt;).select(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;`the.id`&quot;&lt;/span&gt;).show() &lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;IMHO, it is not an issue.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17617481" author="enricomi" created="Fri, 14 Oct 2022 05:36:49 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This issue is about the error message, not the fact that I need to escape &lt;tt&gt;the.id&lt;/tt&gt; in &lt;tt&gt;select&lt;/tt&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17617509" author="ivan.sadikov" created="Fri, 14 Oct 2022 06:31:54 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;It is not clear from the ticket, you should update the description to clarify that this is about the error message.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I don&apos;t see any issues with the error message, &quot;the.id&quot; is unresolved due to the fact that by default this is interpreted as struct field access, not a literal column name. Are you referring to the wrong suggestion in the error message?&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I opened a PR to fix the suggestion list.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
